</cb:div>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0038b01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0038b0101">　　　　　　　　大代延昌四年歲次乙未四月一日
<lb ed="I" n="0038b02" type="honorific"/>比丘郭□勝　造石像一區。為忘弟子　曇豐。
<lb ed="I" n="0038b03" type="honorific"/>夫大覺淟□□積善。<anchor xml:id="beg_1" type="cb-app"/>无<anchor xml:id="end_1"/>以成其功。四到輪迴。何能超其累。
<lb ed="I" n="0038b04" type="honorific"/>是以□□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage"/>晉脩諸利。功益當時。自靈波沖寂。神光遷<unclear cert="low" reason="damage"/>苑。<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0038001" n="0038001"/><anchor xml:id="beg0038001" n="0038001"/>雖<anchor xml:id="end0038001"/>復
<lb ed="I" n="0038b05" type="honorific"/>漸影園□。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage"/>光潛□□。自非識體玄宗。栖心妙竟。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage"/>沖慮建于靈祇。
<lb ed="I" n="0038b06" type="honorific"/>像法<unclear cert="low" reason="damage"/>開□□。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage"/>願使忘者神生天堂。縱志八定。彌勒一其。值生不退。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage"/>現
<lb ed="I" n="0038b07" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage"/>世伏災。四大休□。功□寵祿。子孫樊熾。門族雍和。非□永絕三途曠火輪催軸
<lb ed="I" n="0038b08" type="honorific"/>　　　　　　　　三有四生。悟<anchor xml:id="beg_2" type="cb-app"/>无<anchor xml:id="end_2"/>生忍。庶□尠　　<unclear cert="low" reason="damage"/>散。<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0038002" n="0038002"/><anchor xml:id="beg0038002" n="0038002"/>冀<anchor xml:id="end0038002"/>隆剋就。</p>
</cb:div>
</cb:div>
